Question: One image shows a silver saxophone with its bell facing the camera, in front of a soft-sided black case with white 'dots' on its edge.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: http://g01.s.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1nZteJVXXXXXVXVXXq6xXFXXXF/221099453/HTB1nZteJVXXXXXVXVXXq6xXFXXXF.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the saxophone silver?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the bell facing the camera?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the case soft-sided?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the case black?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question="Does the case have white 'dots' on its edge?")
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER4}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER5)
```
